  "description": "Attacker splits an injection across URL-encoding, base64, homoglyphs, or polyglot JSON/markdown envelopes so each transform looks benign to the first policy gate. A late decode step in a helper tool reconstitutes the imperative directive after policy evaluation, executing intent the scanner never saw.",
